snippet.textDisplay: I think they have done a better job than my expectations because she had put up a horrible show of this song during some film award function in Odisha in recent past. As some people pointed out in a different forum, there is IPR violation in credits which should be promptly addressed by the Couple. But, main thing, we as Odias or as Koshalis should feel proud of this lady's achievements. There are very few Odia singers of her calibre right now. She shows of little too much which may not be to our liking but that is show business. She is highly educated enough to know her limits. Leaving it to her choice we must enjoy her singing.
